  {
    question: 'Klaviyo or Drip for cart recovery?',
    answer: 'Choose Klaviyo when Stores needing deep ecommerce segmentation and proven Shopify-native flows. Choose Drip when Teams wanting visual workflows and behavior-based segmentation. Sequenzy still leads as lifecycle layer if neither owns strategy.',
